biz.paluch.logging.gelf

Interface LogEvent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JBoss7JulLogEvent, JulLogEvent

    public interface LogEvent
    Abstraction for a log event. This interface is usually implemented by a logging framework wrapper to encapsulate the frameworks specifics and expose the required log event details.

    26.09.13 15:16
